source.name: NSF Freedom of Information Act Report for October 1, 1997 through September 30, 1998
source.description: This file contains the National Science Foundation's (NSF's) 1998 FOIA Annual Report. The report provides detailed information regarding the number and type of FOIA cases we processed in FY 1998. It also includes data regarding time and costs associated with processing these cases.
